{"tid":2429120,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳曼琪倡放棄雙重國籍應擴至常秘職級及重要法定機構 (如金管局、保監局等)","createTime":"2021-03-02T05:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T12:40:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":290,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":129,"replies":[{"pid":"f335e8cce530e69de58ea11b4510091b030c0bdb","tid":2429120,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:41:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578282-20210302.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578282-20210302.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQAwp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=0e70d6c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578282-20210302.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7948d3fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578282-20210302.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n全國兩會將於本周召開，一批港區人大代表及政協委員早上出發乘車前往深圳，明日轉飛北京。<br />\n<br />\n港區人大代表團召集人馬逢國表示，未知會議議程有否增減，但若增加討論香港選舉改革，他不會感到意外。他認同回歸多年，無論選委會、立法會或區議會，都是適當時候檢討政制。<br />\n<br />\n另一名港區人大代表陳曼琪說，將提交書面建議，設立公職人員選舉及委任的資格審查法。她認為，目前政府的所有諮詢委員會架構，就任時不需要作出聲明及宣誓，建議將來要擁護《基本法》及效忠香港特區。至於放棄雙重國籍的規定，應擴展至常任秘書長職級，以及重要法定機構，如金管局、保監局等。"},{"pid":"d276f86ef86a68bc3be6fd53c256a3425df1f538","tid":2429120,"uid":79563,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:41:21.000Z","msg":"金管局、保監局要準備宣誓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35dee2162ba7d5813671836d9ce505e4525f7853","tid":2429120,"uid":370972,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:41:51.000Z","msg":"正！keep going"},{"pid":"cf1d0a6bf5f4143580c103c595ca6d7e802b8062","tid":2429120,"uid":51271,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:42:29.000Z","msg":"邵善波同葉劉要剎車架，問過佢未"},{"pid":"0b09434b8a198fd5294eec944c5d1d91426e4bd1","tid":2429120,"uid":127575,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyT