e":"2021-03-02T06:04:43.000Z","msg":"公務員同公營機構都要放棄"},{"pid":"39bcab307ba7c95d673d397f0aecf51334006f55","tid":2429120,"uid":25635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:05:24.000Z","msg":"政協都得<br />\n膠層就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bef8fff2d02f28bf28930de8535cb48aec4bdb1","tid":2429120,"uid":295735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f335e8cce530e69de58ea11b4510091b030c0bdb","tid":2429120,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:41:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578282-20210302.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578282-20210302.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQAwp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=0e70d6c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578282-20210302.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7948d3fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578282-20210302.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n全國兩會將於本周召開，一批港區人大代表及政協委員早上出發乘車前往深圳，明日轉飛北京。<br />\n<br />\n港區人大代表團召集人馬逢國表示，未知會議議程有否增減，但若增加討論香港選舉改革，他不會感到意外。他認同回歸多年，無論選委會、立法會或區議會，都是適當時候檢討政制。<br />\n<br />\n另一名港區人大代表陳曼琪說，將提交書面建議，設立公職人員選舉及委任的資格審查法。她認為，目前政府的所有諮詢委員會架構，就任時不需要作出聲明及宣誓，建議將來要擁護《基本法》及效忠香港特區。至於放棄雙重國籍的規定，應擴展至常任秘書長職級，以及重要法定機構，如金管局、保監局等。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:06:30.000Z","msg":"叫晒d局長。副局長宣誓先。 <br />\n<br />\n之後佢地仔女都一世唔可以離開香港先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08fd13078fb2da33f2de29b85aa1a50b8649aa65","tid":2429120,"uid":33099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c48423b29083c4167c45d274e5c3e3d67ce05596","tid":2429120,"uid":153811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"岩岩hkex 先入左件鬼頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:09:51.000Z","msg":"要佢返工第一日就跪玻璃<br />\n<br />\n佢紅鬚